parameters:
Dynamite Abalone: Wabi wabi... I've had my fill of fun! I
didn't want to dirty the diner, so I made sure to wipe
everything down... Now, shall I take that shark bastard
away!

Memimi: Bunny-chan... I'm sorry I couldn't come to your
aid... But thanks to your sacrifice... our strength is...!

Dynamite Abalone: GYAAAAAAH!!! What the... their
coordination... ugh, the damage...
Abalone Boys: This is bad... Protect Lord Dynamite Abalone!!

Memimi: Bunny-chan... can you move? Thanks to you buying us
time, we were able to come up with a plan! Just one more
push... together...!

Bunny-chan: Of course, Memimi-chan! If I wasn't tough, I
couldn't be a Monster Fight referee! Let's go...!
